      "id": "6ddf9ca6d5dfee4f",
      "text": "The game, Half-Earth Socialism [https://play.half.earth/ site], allows anyone to try their hand as a global planner of a future society. Consider it a sandbox where you can play with a wide range of technologies and policies spanning different fields and ideologies. The game simulates the impact of your decisions by calculating emissions and using a real climate model (HECTOR) to work out the climate effects, while also simulating impacts to the food system and biodiversity, among others."
